        "post_content": "<p>\\r\\n\tMy wife Dyan is working passionately on a film to be projected during performances of my Symphony No. 3 Planet Earth. Please watch the 2-minute video trailer. Can you please share <a href=\"http://www.seedandspark.com/fund/eyethatsees#story\">this</a> within your network?</p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\tThank you for your support! Musically yours,<em> Johan</em></p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\t&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\t&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n",
